      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "eb5409ab-acfd-4ff8-a765-2c38957cf544",
      "text": "Kostya Novoselov led the academic team which overviewed the design, construction and launching of the [[National Graphene Institute]]. He contributed with a number of unique architectural and technical solutions. The veil of the National Graphene Institute depicts formulae from his and Prof. A. Geim early works on graphene. Also, Kostya Novoselov confirms that among the formulae several scientific jokes are hidden, though he has never revealed them."
